<div id="introGroup" class="alt">
	<h1>My Genlighten</h1>
	<h2>Your dashboard and homebase within Genlighten</h2>
	<p>This page will serve as your primary starting point at Genlighten.com, allowing you to access the site&#146;s key features, whether 
		you&#146;re a lookup client, a provider, or both. If you need help using our site, feel free to visit our <a href="<%=help_user_url(@user)%>">help page</a>.</p>
	</div>

	<div class="dbColumn">
		<h1>Find Documents</h1>
